{"tid":650558,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"長和小米擬合組全球策略同盟　明開記招交代","createTime":"2018-05-02T12:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T08:45:59.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f083af1d38e0b568ba377c9f6e5ab7734b8ff41d","tid":650558,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:37:00.000Z","msg":"長和繼早前同馬雲旗下螞蟻金服組成策略同盟，在港推廣支付寶HK業務後，盛傳將於本周開記者會，同在本港上市的小米合組全球策略同盟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長和向傳媒發出採訪通知，將會在 5 月 3 日舉行記者招待會，屆時將會有長和集團聯席董事總經理霍建寧，以及小米高級副總裁王翔出席。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，雙方將在業務上展開合作，暫不涉及股權交易。港交所在 4 月 30 日起接受「同股不同權」企業提交上市申請，市場估計小米將會在本周內遞交上市申請。根據公開資料表示，王翔於 2015 年加入小米，之前任高通全球高級副總裁兼大中華區總裁，曾與小米在晶片供應上合作過。"},{"pid":"42234f052b0981a9cd05e4e7a4fd9d67d48d553e","tid":650558,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:42:27.000Z","msg":"誠哥祝福"},{"pid":"b5d945ca9c073fe5d2520b79f2337962d9befb03","tid":650558,"uid":63211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"應該同誠哥旗下商場同電訊搞物聯網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030a1bc1e46739fd15caf05dade382f2d692eae6","tid":650558,"uid":19933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"應酬下你班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2ab6f9f72526001607706c90c7745787e16b49","tid":650558,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5d945ca9c073fe5d2520b79f2337962d9befb03","tid":650558,"uid":63211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"應該同誠哥旗下商場同電訊搞物聯網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:01:47.000Z","msg":"誠哥商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2aad3f2a5bc996e94b3b0c3bf6fa546c75dec0","tid":650558,"uid":63211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5d945ca9c073fe5d2520b79f2337962d9befb03","tid":650558,"uid":